Window
show/hide launch bar = option + cmd + d
Focus to the apple on the menu bar = ctrl +f4 (changed from default of ctrl +f2 which wouldnâ€™t work consistently)
minimize = cmd + M


Navigation
fn + left arrow = begin of doc
fn + right arrow = end of doc
cmd + left arrow = begin of line
cmd + right arrow = end of line
page-up = alt + up arrow
page-down = alt + down arrow

Text editing
delete text to left of cursor = delete
delete text to right of cursor = fn + delete
